# Progress Tracking
- [ ] Open dashboard.html in the browser.
- [ ] Wait for page load and capture initial screenshot (Tổng quan).
- [ ] Naviate to "Tài khoản" tab and capture screenshot.
- [ ] Navigate to "Models" tab and capture screenshot.
- [ ] Navigate to "Cấu hình" tab and capture screenshot.
- [ ] Check console logs for errors (CORS, etc.).
- [ ] Final report.
